{"tid":2142462,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"小夫我就不出去了 - 曾志豪","createTime":"2020-08-06T12:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T12:00:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"12962a04b8b0d7569b2524a87f38529d802aadcb","tid":2142462,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T12:00:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200723/ANBLZ2N2URAA3IOX2H7Z76JWI4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200723%2FANBLZ2N2URAA3IOX2H7Z76JWI4%2F&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOhSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=48013e04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200723%2FANBLZ2N2URAA3IOX2H7Z76JWI4%2F&h=b90f245e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200723/ANBLZ2N2URAA3IOX2H7Z76JWI4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n小夫我就不出去了 - 曾志豪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ufCx2_3P9-zyC5Wike4Alo4IvTs=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KQZEXPZAU5C4BDDZTI46QEBLTI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FufCx2_3P9-zyC5Wike4Alo4IvTs%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKQZEXPZAU5C4BDDZTI46QEBLTI.jpg&h=fb09fae2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幻覺嚟嘅啫，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n。一個叫做禾野男孩的內地同人漫畫家，畫了一輯《哆啦AV夢》的惡搞漫畫，把叮噹（改不了口）的純真風格變成18禁男男同志畫面，大玩屎及不同體液，再加上技安和阿福（即係小夫）合體變「四腳獸」，一句「小夫我要進來了」，破壞力比起「光時」這種口號更危害國家安全及心智發展。<br />\n<br />\n事情鬧大了，內地當然不容這種毀三觀的作品存活，全網封殺，禾野男孩也無奈出來認低威，表態要支持共建綠色網絡環境。相反台灣對這種漫畫表現大方，內政部甚至出post抽水，網友也是一笑置之。<br />\n<br />\n香港的黃Ｇ鋒也借題發揮，覺得強國打壓同人創作的自由，為表不滿，攬炒地上載了原裝多啦A夢的一些漫畫情節，竟然是大雄開坦克車、而技安（胖虎）提兩個膠袋擋在坦克車前&hellip;&hellip;Ｇ鋒擺明想強國最好連原裝叮噹都封殺。<br />\n<br />\n當大家都以為劇本。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n受害人突然變成加。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n或許他是受到壓力、。。。。。。。。。"}]}